text: Hornskrokens IF is a sports club in Boden, Sweden. It was established on 23 May 1933Hornskroken IF 80 Ã¥r, accessdate: 13 October 2013 It runs handball. It earlier even ran bandy, soccer, orienteering and skiing. In 1983, the club played in the qualifying rounds for the Handball Allsvenskan. The women's soccer team played five seasons in the Swedish top division between 1978-1986. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1933 establishments in Europe Category:Handball clubs in Sweden Category:Swedish football clubs Category:Bandy clubs in Sweden Category:Ski clubs in Sweden Category:1930s establishments in Sweden
